      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and we want to be fully transparent about its state before you consider purchasing. The exterior shows significant wear including multiple deep scratches, noticeable dents, and considerable paint fading and chipping across various panels. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard components, and general deterioration consistent with heavy use over many years. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues and will likely require meaningful repairs \u2014 this is reflected honestly in the asking price. This car is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs basic transportation and is comfortable with the associated risks and repair costs. We strongly recommend a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic before committing to this purchase.",
