    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and the price reflects that reality honestly. The car has significant mechanical and cosmetic issues that will require serious attention \u2014 buyers should expect to invest in repairs before this vehicle is fully reliable. It may still be drivable in its current state, but it is not recommended for daily use without addressing the underlying problems first. Visible wear is present throughout the interior and exterior, and one or more major mechanical systems \u2014 such as the engine, transmission, suspension, or brakes \u2014 are in need of repair or replacement. This listing is best suited for a mechanically skilled buyer, a hobbyist looking for a project car, or someone who intends to use it for parts. There are no misrepresentations here: you are purchasing a vehicle that needs substantial work, priced accordingly.",
