      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in truly mint condition \u2014 an exceptionally rare find on the used market. The exterior is virtually flawless, showcasing deep, lustrous paint with no visible scratches, chips, or dents. Every panel aligns perfectly, and the chrome and trim pieces are pristine. Inside, the cabin looks and feels as though it just rolled off the showroom floor \u2014 seats, carpets, headliner, and all surfaces are immaculate with no wear, stains, or odors. All electronics, controls, and infotainment systems function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, with no leaks, no unusual noises, and strong, confident performance. The tires have excellent tread remaining, and the brakes are in top shape. Service records are available and reflect consistent, thorough maintenance throughout the vehicle's life. If you're looking for a used car that truly feels new, this is it \u2014 you will not be disappointed.",
